{"tid":1826883,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[集中討論] ONEPIECE 海賊王 第968話 漫畫情報","createTime":"2020-01-16T13:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T09:50:20.000Z","uid":130563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"412aada820dc731c76e063eaab1dabdcec7d7287","tid":1826883,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:19:36.000Z","msg":"968話標題 御田歸來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YF8hpm0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYF8hpm0.jpg&h=e71149e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n世人把羅傑得到的所有東西稱為「連成一片的大秘寶」ONE PIECE。<br />\n（註：之前多譯為「獨一無二的大秘寶」）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t9wZCN7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft9wZCN7.jpg&h=0087bcc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【面對從拉夫德爾返回的羅傑，紅太郎（後無）】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tFr2eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tFr2eR.jpg&h=14671364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【當然，我們是笑著離別的，因為總有一天我們還會再見！】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aSXerGC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaSXerGC.jpg&h=048569d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【等一下，御田先生，如果因為這種事情動怒&hellip;&hellip;又會遭到敵人的反擊（後無）】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j8e8v8m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj8e8v8m.jpg&h=51264c16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cb2BE1T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCb2BE1T.jpg&h=e04ae41b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【大蛇：等等！御田先&hellip;&hellip;御田！好好想想！要是砍了我凱多可不會無動於衷！<br />\n好好想想這個國家會發生什麼！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h8wuZ2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh8wuZ2b.jpg&h=54d8d45c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n御田：先斬了再想<br />\n大蛇（對哦，這傢伙是個瘋子！）】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NLU06HO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNLU06HO.jpg&h=8403dbd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;然後會逐漸超過我們！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;我們&hellip;&hellip;來的太早了，ONE PIECE會被誰找到呢<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;那肯定是我兒子吧<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;你哪有兒子<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;之後會有的<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;哇哈哈哈哈<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;好啊！喝一杯吧！向著沒有海軍的大海出發！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;我第一個下船！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;然後歡送御田<br />\n（註：這段台詞源自劇場版stampede最後的彩蛋對話，本話漫畫有所補充。）<br />\n下周不休刊。"},{"pid":"aca1c1ab820b3b7400a767abb14556a16338191d","tid":1826883,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:22:13.000Z","msg":"終於有了 等咗好耐"},{"pid":"78780877f98058dbaf968dfd8b6843a891594125","tid":1826883,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"有個問題 點解凱多要咁幫大蛇<br />\n點解凱多唔直接殺咗大蛇要己做將軍？"},{"pid":"7f5310061e5796cd59f4c83176be46c8df12fdbd","tid":1826883,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:01:42.000Z","msg":"【（大蛇）驚叫<br />\n大蛇將軍請回答！！】<br />\n【時：沒關係的，御田先生，我的傷也已經痊癒了！<br />\n御田：你被箭射中了嗎&hellip;&hellip;！感謝你&hellip;&hellip;盡力保護了我們的孩子！肯定很痛吧！<br />\n時：等等御田先生，如果因為這種事情動怒&hellip;&hellip;又會遭到敵人的反擊<br />\n御田：這種事情？阿時，你還沒聽說過我的「往事」吧&hellip;&hellip;】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YRF0nva.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYRF0nva.jpg&h=12d7758a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c59b6c6d0bcb76c09e41188ae6bebdd816d69e66","tid":1826883,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:04:16.000Z","msg":"雖然有劇場版reference 但係成個回憶都唔覺見到巴雷特"},{"pid":"c75a70249aec76325036634e1f7efc261b9c0b2d","tid":1826883,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78780877f98058dbaf968dfd8b6843a891594125","tid":1826883,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"有個問題 點解凱多要咁幫大蛇<br />\n點解凱多唔直接殺咗大蛇要己做將軍？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:39:52.000Z","msg":"陣營對立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5303180177cfb94e1c96bfe96